name: Competitors are friends
description: Hey, my acquaintance is hipi. Hipi is a story about a cellphone seller who has many friends. Sometimes, cheated by his own friends. However, he is still tough because a seller's sustenance is completely beyond human control. God meet good people who want to help Hipi get up again selling. And a good friend reminded him to keep positive thinking. Because your kindness will return to yourself.
